ZH: 我完全赞成你的观点。
EN: I fully agree with your point of view.

ZH: 我赞成政府采取更多环保措施。
EN: I support the government taking more environmental measures.

ZH: 很多人赞成这项改革。
EN: Many people are in favor of this reform.

ZH: 我不能赞成你的决定。
EN: I cannot endorse your decision.

ZH: 他赞成这个计划的实施。
EN: He approves the implementation of this plan.

ZH: 总统赞成取消这项法律。
EN: The president supports the repeal of this law.

ZH: 这个决策得到了大家的赞成。
EN: This decision has received everyone's approval.

ZH: 他们都赞成你的想法。
EN: They all agree with your idea.

ZH: 比尔向我们寻求赞成。
EN: Bill seeks our approval.

ZH: 我对这个提议表示赞成。
EN: I express my agreement with this proposal.

ZH: 即使我不赞成，我也会尊重你的选择。
EN: Even if I don't agree, I will still respect your choice.

ZH: 请你给出一个赞成或反对的意见。
EN: Please give your opinion of approval or disapproval.

ZH: 他丝毫没有赞成他父亲的决定。
EN: He did not support his father's decision at all.

ZH: 我们需要获得他们的赞成才能进行改变。
EN: We need their approval to make the changes.

ZH: 老师的赞成对我很重要。
EN: The teacher's approval is important to me.

ZH: 她与我完全赞成你的意见。
EN: She agrees with your opinion completely, just like me.

ZH: 我不能说我完全赞成你的观点。
EN: I can't say that I fully agree with your point of view.

ZH: 他赞成禁止吸烟。
EN: He is in favor of banning smoking.

ZH: 你能不能赞成我们的建议？
EN: Can you endorse our recommendation?

ZH: 我不能赞成你的做法。
EN: I cannot approve of your actions.
